msgid "# New-AdfsLdapServerConnection"
msgstr "# 新的 AdfsLdapServer 连接"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Creates a connection object."
msgstr "创建一个连接对象。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The **New-AdfsLdapServerConnection** cmdlet creates a connection object that represents the Lightweight Directory Access Protocol (LDAP) folder that serves as a claims provider trust.\n"
"A connection object includes host name, port, and authentication credentials."
msgstr ""
"`New-AdfsLdapServerConnection` cmdlet "
"创建一个连接对象，该对象代表用于充当声明提供者信任的轻量级目录访问协议（LDAP）文件夹。连接对象包含主机名、端口和身份验证凭据。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Create an LDAP connection"
msgstr "### 示例 1：创建一个 LDAP 连接"

msgid ""
"The first command prompts you for a user name and password by using the **Get-Credential** cmdlet.\n"
"The command stores the results in the $Credential variable."
msgstr ""
"第一个命令使用 `Get-Credential` cmdlet 来提示用户输入用户名和密码，并将结果存储在 `$Credential` 变量中。"

msgid ""
"The second command creates an LDAP connection.\n"
"DomainContoller03.contoso.com is the fully qualified domain name of a domain controller in the other forest.\n"
"The command stores the result in the $LdapConn variable."
msgstr ""
"第二个命令用于创建一个LDAP连接。DomainController03.contoso.com是另一个森林（forest）中某个域控制器的完全限定域名（fully"
" qualified domain name）。该命令将连接结果存储在$LdapConn变量中。"

msgid ""
"To see this cmdlet as part of creating an LDAP local claims provider trust, "
"see the **Add-AdfsLocalClaimsProviderTrust** cmdlet."
msgstr ""
"要了解此 cmdlet 是如何用于创建 LDAP 本地声明提供程序信任关系的，请参阅 **Add-"
"AdfsLocalClaimsProviderTrust** cmdlet。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the authentication method the local claims provider trust uses.\n"
"In Windows Server 2016, the only supported method is Basic (username/password)."
msgstr "指定本地声明提供者所信任的身份验证方法。在 Windows Server 2016 中，唯一支持的方法是基本身份验证（用户名/密码）。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the credentials to use for the connection to the LDAP host.\n"
"To obtain a **PSCredential** object, use the **Get-Credential** cmdlet."
msgstr ""
"指定用于连接 LDAP 主机的凭据。要获取一个 **PSCredential** 对象，请使用 **Get-Credential** cmdlet。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the fully qualified domain name of the server that hosts the LDAP "
"folder to which Active Directory Federation Services (AD FS) connects for "
"authentication requests."
msgstr ""
"指定托管LDAP文件夹的服务器的完全限定域名。Active Directory Federation Services（AD "
"FS）会连接到该服务器以发送身份验证请求。"

msgid "Specifies the port that AD FS uses to connect to the LDAP host."
msgstr "指定 AD FS 用于连接到 LDAP 主机的端口。"

msgid ""
"Specifies SSL setting of the connection.\n"
"The acceptable values for this parameter are:"
msgstr "指定连接的 SSL 设置。该参数的可接受值为："

